    <h1>About Foodies</h1>
    <p>Foodies is an online delivery application created for the ECE_CK802 Internet Programming Course within the ECE department of the University of Patras located in Greece.</p>
    <p>Our mission is to provide a convenient platform for users to order food from their favorite restaurants and have it delivered to their doorstep.</p>
    <p>With Foodies, you can explore a variety of cuisines, place orders, track deliveries, and enjoy delicious meals without leaving your home.</p>
    
